Description: Desktop environment customisation for Debian
 Installs all Debian packages, both essential dependencies
 as well as recommended packages and applications.
 Installs:
   Debian Budgie panel configuration
   gsettings overrides
   applies the default Gtk+ theme & icon-theme for GTK+
   applications

